---
// About tab panel body: avatar + short mono bio (condensed from Stanley's copy).
---

<div class="about">
  <img
    class="about__avatar"
    src="/avatar.jpg"
    width="112"
    height="112"
    alt="Stanley Tejakusuma avatar"
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
  />
  <div class="about__bio">
    <p>
      Hey hey! I'm Stanley. I live and breathe data, working between the blockchain and analytics
      space. Started out as a data scientist and it became a habit I can't shake: markets,
      blockchains, models, even my own routines all look like datasets to me. Sometimes I break
      things along the way, but that's part of the learning curve 😉.
    </p>
    <p>
      I rarely stop at the analysis. I build the pipelines that collect the data, the models that
      learn from it, and the tools that act upon it — and I care a ton about making them simple
      enough to actually trust.
    </p>
    <p>
      Off the clock: a Tennis or Padel court, or the nearest mountain in Java. Stay hungry, stay
      foolish.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    max-width: 72ch;
  }

  .about__avatar {
    flex: none;
    width: clamp(76px, 9vw, 96px);
    height: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .about__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-fg) 72%, var(--color-muted));
  }

  .about__bio p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about__bio p + p {
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .about {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
